#|_   _|__ _ __ _ __ ___ (_)_ __   __ _| |
  #| |/ _ \ '__| '_ ` _ \| | '_ \ / _` | |
  #| |  __/ |  | | | | | | | | | | (_| | |
  #|_|\___|_|  |_| |_| |_|_|_| |_|\__,_|_|

# Workspace for terminal
bspc rule -a Alacritty desktop=^1 follow=on focus=on


#  ___   __  __ _
# / _ \ / _|/ _(_) ___ ___
#| | | | |_| |_| |/ __/ _ \
#| |_| |  _|  _| | (_|  __/
